      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Kings 17:21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Which they had made - \"Which\" refers to \"statutes.\" The lsraelites had \"walked in the statutes of the pagan, and in those of the kings of Israel, which (statutes) they (the kings) had made.\" ",
        "children": [
